                "in the center, NaI(Tl) detector of 4inch diameter and",
                "6 inch length.",
                "Energy resolution 1.62 kev (FWHM).",
                "Energy calibration was done by",
                "Co-57(121.94,136.31 keV), Cs-137(661.595 keV),",
                "Zr-95(724.24 keV), Nb-95(765.84 keV),",
                "Ir-192(205.782,295.938,308.429,316.486,468.053,588.557,",
                "604.385,612.435 keV), Mn-54(834.78 keV),",
                "Y-88(898.09 keV), Na-22, Na-24,",
